00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.000
Okay.

00:09:46.333 --> 00:09:48.833
Okay, we're ready to begin.

00:09:49.333 --> 00:09:51.875
Thank you for joining us.

00:09:53.666 --> 00:09:54.500
Yes.

00:09:55.333 --> 00:09:56.458
Oh.

