00:10:06.708 --> 00:10:09.541
is what they're saying.

00:10:10.916 --> 00:10:11.916
Okay.

00:10:14.416 --> 00:10:16.750
As you all know,

00:10:17.250 --> 00:10:22.250
conducting the whole process
from roasting to melanging

00:10:22.333 --> 00:10:24.833
would take us about four days.

00:10:24.916 --> 00:10:31.166
So I've been given
pre-blocked chocolate for today.

00:10:31.666 --> 00:10:32.541
Is it in here?

00:10:34.375 --> 00:10:35.500
Oh, here it is.

00:10:38.125 --> 00:10:38.958
Here you go.

00:10:39.458 --> 00:10:40.750
Thank you.

00:10:41.583 --> 00:10:43.541
Careful, it's hot.

00:10:50.708 --> 00:10:53.208
Oh, now! Please check the temperature…

00:10:54.541 --> 00:10:57.166
is what they're saying.

00:11:34.875 --> 00:11:37.208
It's the same Pure Kenji we know.

00:11:38.250 --> 00:11:39.416
That's a relief.

00:11:40.041 --> 00:11:41.541
It's really good.

00:11:42.041 --> 00:11:43.791
Mind if I try one too?

00:11:43.875 --> 00:11:44.708
Go ahead.

00:11:48.291 --> 00:11:49.333
Thanks.

00:11:56.916 --> 00:11:58.166
It's delicious.

00:12:22.708 --> 00:12:26.791
Thank you so much
for sharing your precious recipe.

00:12:26.875 --> 00:12:28.791
Thank you!

00:12:28.875 --> 00:12:30.041
It's my pleasure.

00:12:30.125 --> 00:12:33.125
Please do your best
in making the best chocolate…

00:12:34.416 --> 00:12:35.916
is what they said.

00:12:37.916 --> 00:12:43.250
Okay, I'd like to end our remote call
with the Anonymous Chocolatier.

00:12:43.333 --> 00:12:44.708
We appreciate your time.

00:12:44.791 --> 00:12:46.583
Thank you for your time!

00:12:48.041 --> 00:12:49.500
Great work, everyone.

00:12:49.583 --> 00:12:50.791
Thank you.

00:12:50.875 --> 00:12:52.166
-Thank you.
-Thanks!

00:12:55.166 --> 00:12:57.250
Chief, go crush the competition.

00:12:57.333 --> 00:12:58.583
I got this.

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:47.750
